---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — AgentleConsulting"
  description="AgentleConsulting Terms of Service. Terms governing the use of our automation consulting services.">

  <div class="bg-cream py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-site max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl text-slate mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate/50 mb-12">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate/75 space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Scope of Services</h2>
          <p>AgentleConsulting provides custom automation consulting and implementation services for Amazon and Bol.com sellers. Our services include workflow analysis, automation system design, implementation, testing, and handover of automated workflows.</p>
          <p>Specific deliverables are outlined in individual proposals and statements of work signed by both parties.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Client Responsibilities</h2>
          <p>Clients are responsible for providing timely access to relevant platforms, APIs, and documentation required to deliver the services. Clients must ensure they have the right to automate the workflows discussed and hold valid accounts on the relevant marketplaces.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Pricing and Payment</h2>
          <p>All pricing is fixed per engagement model as published on this website or as quoted in a signed proposal. We do not charge hourly rates for the Deliverables described in your proposal.</p>
          <p>Payment terms: 50% upon project commencement, 50% upon final delivery. For projects over €10,000, milestone-based payment schedules may apply as specified in the proposal.</p>
          <p>All amounts are in Euros (€) and exclusive of Dutch VAT where applicable.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>Upon full payment, clients receive ownership of the automation workflows built specifically for them, including associated documentation. AgentleConsulting retains rights to general frameworks, templates, and methodologies not specific to the client's business.</p>
          <p>We reserve the right to showcase general project descriptions (without confidential business details) in our portfolio and marketing materials.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Confidentiality</h2>
          <p>Both parties agree to keep confidential any proprietary information disclosed during the engagement. This includes business data, workflows, sales volumes, supplier information, and technical specifications. Confidentiality obligations survive for 3 years after the end of the engagement.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Service Level and Warranty</h2>
          <p>All deliverables undergo sandbox testing before handover. We provide a bug-fix warranty period post-handover as specified in your package (30 days for Automate, 90 days for Transform). Warranty covers malfunction of the delivered automation due to defects in our work — not changes to third-party APIs, marketplace rule changes, or modifications made by the client.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Our total liability for any claim arising from our services shall not exceed the total fees paid by the client for the specific deliverable giving rise to the claim. We are not liable for indirect damages, lost profits, lost data, or consequential losses.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Termination</h2>
          <p>Either party may terminate an engagement with 14 days written notice. In case of termination:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Client pays for all work completed up to the termination date</li>
            <li>Client receives all completed deliverables for which payment has been received</li>
            <li>We deliver a partial handover report for any work in progress</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by Dutch law. Disputes will be subject to the jurisdiction of the courts of Amsterdam, Netherlands.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-slate">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>AgentleConsulting</strong><br/>
            Amsterdam, Netherlands<br/>
            <a href="mailto:hello@agentleconsulting.com" class="text-sage">hello@agentleconsulting.com</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
